END, [p.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [p.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [p.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [p.ProductCategory].[HomeOrder], [p.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [p.ProductCategory].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag0], [p.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [p.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [p.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords] AS [Seokeywords0], [p.ProductCategory].[Status] AS [Status0], [p.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [p.ProductCategory].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [p.ProductCategory].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [p.ProductCategory].[Id]

END, [p.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [p.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [p.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [p.ProductCategory].[HomeOrder], [p.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [p.ProductCategory].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag0], [p.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [p.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [p.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords] AS [Seokeywords0], [p.ProductCategory].[Status] AS [Status0], [p.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [p.ProductCategory].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [p.ProductCategory].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [p.ProductCategory].[Id]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p.ProductCategory] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [p.ProductCategory].[Id]
WHERE [p].[Status] = 1
ORDER BY [p].[DateCreated] DESC
OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY" (0723d8ff)
